    <license>PHP License</license>
    <state>stable</state>
    <notes>* Removed a workaround for a bug in the Reflection API in PHP 5.0.0 in
  PHPUnit2_Framework_TestCase::runTest().

- Removed references to the PHPUnit2_TestDox package which has been merged
  into the PHPUnit2 package for the upcoming PHPUnit2-2.1.X release family.

! PHPUnit now requires PHP 5.0.1 (or higher).</notes>
